msgid "# triton.language.device_assert"
msgstr "# triton.language.device_assert"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/device_assert.md:2
msgid "**使用`device_assert`需要将环境变量`TRITON_DEBUG`的值设置为非`0`才能生效。**"
msgstr "**Using `device_assert` requires setting the environment variable `TRITON_DEBUG` to a non-zero value to take effect.**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/device_assert.md:4
msgid "## 1. 函数概述"
msgstr "## 1. Function Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/device_assert.md:6
msgid "`device_assert` 用于在GPU运行时从设备端进行断言检查，如果条件不满足则输出错误信息。"
msgstr "`device_assert` is used to perform assertion checks from the device side during GPU runtime, outputting an error message if the condition is not met."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/device_assert.md:8
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.device_assert(cond, msg='', _semantic=None)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/device_assert.md:10
msgid "## 2. 规格"
msgstr "## 2. Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/device_assert.md:12
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/device_assert.md:14
msgid ""
"| 参数 | 类型 | 默认值 | 含义说明 |\n"
"|------|------|--------|----------|\n"
"| `cond` | `bool` | 必需 | 运行时需要断言的条件表达式 |\n"
"| `msg` | `str` | `''` | 断言失败时显示的错误消息 |\n"
"| `_semantic` | - | - | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter | Type | Default | Description |\n"
"|-----------|------|---------|-------------|\n"
"| `cond` | `bool` | Required | The condition expression to assert at runtime |\n"
"| `msg` | `str` | `''` | Error message displayed when assertion fails |\n"
"| `_semantic` | - | - | Reserved parameter, external calls not supported for now |\n"

